parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Inadequate Rust Protection of Structural Components

loss of structural integrity.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of rear struts can cause the vehicle to lose handling and stability, leading to accidents or injuries.

sagging of the rear of the vehicle.
